WEBVTT

00:10:26.186 --> 00:10:32.087
ED: So this is the kind of helping
that human beings evolved to enjoy,

00:10:32.111 --> 00:10:34.022
but for 40 years,

00:10:34.046 --> 00:10:36.493
Canada was the only country in the world

00:10:36.517 --> 00:10:39.977
that allowed private citizens
to sponsor refugees.

00:10:40.565 --> 00:10:42.749
Now -- Canada!

00:10:42.773 --> 00:10:44.933
(Applause)

00:10:44.957 --> 00:10:46.273
It's pretty great.

00:10:47.354 --> 00:10:50.900
Now Australia and the UK
are starting up similar programs.

00:10:51.613 --> 00:10:55.116
Just imagine how different
the refugee crisis could look

00:10:55.140 --> 00:10:57.599
if more countries made this possible.

00:10:58.647 --> 00:11:02.628
Creating these kinds of meaningful
connections between individuals